seedu.addressbook.data

Class AddressBook

  • java.lang.Object
    • seedu.addressbook.data.AddressBook

  • public class AddressBook
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the entire address book. Contains the data of the address book. Guarantees: - Every tag found in every person will also be found in the tag list. - The tags in each person point to tag objects in the master list. (== equality)

      • addPerson

        public void addPerson(Person toAdd)
               throws UniquePersonList.DuplicatePersonException
        Adds a person to the address book. Also checks the new person's tags and updates allTags with any new tags found, and updates the Tag objects in the person to point to those in allTags.
        Throws:
        UniquePersonList.DuplicatePersonException - if an equivalent person already exists.
